*** lancement
npm i
node server.js

*** docker :

-docker file
docker build -t toto/titi
docker run --name toto -p 8080:3000

-docker-compose
production : docker-compose -f docker/docker-compose.yml up -d,
build : docker-compose -f docker/docker-compose.yml build


*** URL :
http://localhost:8080/


*** mysql
-installer phpmyadmin
-installer le module node mysql


